    <h1 align="center", style="background-color: coral;"><b>HTML</b></h1>
    <p>HyperText Markup Language or HTML is used for defining a structure or layout of a website or an application.</p>
    <p>The code maily consists of two sections: HEAD and BODY.</p>
    <h3>HEAD</h3>
    <p>In this section, we can define the title of the webpage.</p>
    <h3>BODY</h3>
    <p>In this section, we can align text, change the font of the text we inserted and also we can design a background color for the text.</p>
</body>
